# seq_api_key (Resource)

Use this resource to create and manage API keys in Seq via `/api/apikeys`.

Seq may only return the key `token` at creation time; it is stored in Terraform state as a sensitive attribute.

## Example Usage

### Basic API Key

```terraform
resource "seq_api_key" "ingest" {
  title       = "terraform-ingest"
  permissions = ["Ingest"]
}
```

### API Key with Input Settings

```terraform
resource "seq_api_key" "app_ingest" {
  title         = "my-application"
  permissions   = ["Ingest"]
  minimum_level = "Warning"
  filter        = "@Level = 'Error' or @Level = 'Fatal'"
  
  applied_properties = {
    Application = "MyApp"
    Environment = "Production"
  }
}
```

